{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'm sure that they must have had something, a plank or something, to go up there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So of course, you know, like mothers, I remember my mother, you know, trying to help in the car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, help, you know, the younger children, the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't even recall, you know, as far as food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They must have had some, some food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they did bring up water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then of course, you know, they had-- in the car there was some provision, you know, to relieve yourselves, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What kind of provision?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They must have had some kind of-- I don't exactly recall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't let you out for that matter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, younger children-- you know, I mean, children, I mean, we-- Jewish children, for some reason or other, we were sort of-- how shall I say?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were conditioned, you know, in situations like that, not to complain and not to cry or anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my youngest sister was five, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I mean, it was a very, very morbid, you know, situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody was this-- I don't remember or recall discussing anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it took about-- I remember, for some reason or other, I remember-- not exactly, but we must've gone to the-- in the direction of Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I remember a town, you know, like Presov.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember, you know, they had rolling hills, you know, with beautiful grass.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was in the springtime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you could see out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was some, some-- you know, with bars, bars, but--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Windows, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Windows with bars.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
